# iGLA v6 IMMORTAL FUSION - All v6 Technologies Combined
# The Ultimate Fusion: 15000x TARGET
# φ² + 1/φ² = 3 | КОЩЕЙ БЕССМЕРТЕН | PHOENIX = 999

name: igla_v6_immortal_fusion
version: "6.0.0"
language: zig
module: igla_v6_immortal_fusion

types:
  ImmortalConfig:
    fields:
      mixture_agents: Bool
      self_speculative: Bool
      sparse_attention: Bool
      neural_kv: Bool
      fp4_adaptive: Bool
      distributed: Bool
      spec_rag: Bool
      layer_skip: Bool
      medusa2: Bool
      bitnet: Bool
      grouped_gemm: Bool
      quantum_ready: Bool
      
  ImmortalState:
    fields:
      active_features: Int
      total_speedup: Float
      immortal_mode: Bool
      
  PhoenixResurrection:
    fields:
      resurrection_count: Int
      last_resurrection: Int
      immortal_verified: Bool

behaviors:
  - name: immortal_init
    given: "All v6 features"
    when: "Initialization"
    then: "IMMORTAL MODE activated"
    
  - name: multi_agent_layer
    given: "MoA enabled"
    when: "Agent collaboration"
    then: "3x quality boost"
    
  - name: extreme_quantization
    given: "BitNet + FP4"
    when: "Quantization"
    then: "10x memory reduction"
    
  - name: ultra_decode
    given: "Medusa2 + Self-Spec + Layer Skip"
    when: "Decoding"
    then: "8x decode speedup"
    
  - name: infinite_scale
    given: "Distributed + Sparse + Neural KV"
    when: "Scaling"
    then: "Unlimited scale"
    
  - name: phoenix_resurrection
    given: "Any failure"
    when: "Auto-recovery"
    then: "Immortal operation"

immortal_formula:
  v5_phoenix: 5000
  v6_multiplier: 3
  target: "5000 × 3 = 15000x"
  
sacred_constants:
  phi: 1.618033988749895
  trinity: 3
  phoenix: 999
  immortal: "∞"
